  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The GoldenEye story comes to life once again with an updated single player storyline featuring Daniel Craig as Bond and written by Bruce Feirstein, the screenwriter for the original movie.\n\nSurprise enemies covertly or engage in a full on firefight and use Bond's latest gadget to uncover intel in augmented reality as you relive all the classic GoldenEye movie moments. Infiltrate the dam and destroy the facility; chase Ourumov in the tank through the streets of St. Petersburgh; and investigate the secret jungle base.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "The story of the DS version of GoldenEye follows the same general story as the Wii version although the levels have a different layout. The Nightclub level was dropped, and Airfield is a short cutscene at the end of Facility.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
